      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The suit which A. Kiblan started\nagainst the Northern Pacific has been\nsettled and compromised out OF court\nand the attorneys have asked that\nthe case be dismissed.\n\n\nKiblan was a commercial traveller\nand alleged in his complaint that the\nrailway people had refused to handle\nhis trunk from Spokane to Tyler.\nwash, and had refused to return 1t\nTO him after he had checked It\nthrough.\n\n\nThe trunk contained samples valued\nMt $52910. the amount of damages\nfor which he brought suit,"
    }
